  "description": "<p>Working Hours:<br>\nMon–Fri: 8:30am–5:30pm<br>\nSat: 8:30am–1:00pm<br>\nRest Days: 6 days/month</p>\n<p>Company: Import &amp; delivery services — mainly local and port deliveries.<br>\n<br>\nJob Scope:<br>\n<br>\nDrive 24ft truck from port to designated locations<br>\n<br>\nNo overtime, finish work on time<br>\n<br>\nFollow supervisor’s instructions, not picky with tasks<br>\n<br>\nRequirements:<br>\n<br>\nMust hold a valid Singapore Class 4 Driving Licence<br>\n<br>\nFamiliar with Singapore roads<br>\n<br>\nPhysically fit and healthy<br>\n<br>\nBenefits:<br>\n<br>\nParking available near home for heavy vehicles<br>\n<br>\nAnnual leave, medical leave &amp; performance bonus after probation<br>\n<br>\nWork Location: Islandwide (Company at Tanjong Pagar)<br>\n<br>\nLEE LAI MUN R1657696</p>",
